    "problemStatement": "Good Number\n\nProblem Statement\n\nGiven a digit an a range . Write a program to print all the good numbers between range and that do not contain given digit\n\nNote: A good number is a number in which every digit is larger than the sum of digits of its right\n\nExample: 9421 is a good number\n\n          9 > (4+2+1)\n\n          4 > (2+1)\n\n          2 > 1",
